TopicTitle: Get to Mun or Minmus in time

Articles.Content:
eyecikjou's Challenges:

Challenge 1:

Land on the mun in 5 hours of mission time.

Challenge 2:

Land on the mun in 3 hours of mission time and return in 3 hours to kerbin

Challenge 3:

Land on minmus in 5 hours in mission time

Challenge 4:

Land on minmus in 4 hours in mission time and return in 4 hours to kerbin

Challenge 5:

Land on the mun then land on minmus and return back to kerbin in a total mission time of 18 hours

How to proof:

Make a video and upload to youtube.
